title: Convolver Viper4AndroidWindows
description:
These are my collections of .irs (impulse response sample) audio effects files to be used in conjunction with viper4android or viper4windows. you can find more information from these websites:

Windows:
 
http://vipersaudio.com/blog/?page_id=59

Android:
 
http://forum.xda-developers.com/showthread.php?t=2191223

If you like the audio effects or app or software, please make some donations to the developer(s).

there are various settings within the application to make your audio effects, be it listening to songs or watching a movie, rendering out spectacularly superb audio effects. try it out, you will love it.

Please seed as long as you can, tq
